{"tid":2022541,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"長文有圖)ig上可憐貓貓搶食金拱門炸雞翼之對鬧","createTime":"2020-05-18T11:28:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T21:00:06.000Z","uid":346359,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6fcf716c378bacff48af62a9ad8a759e06747146","tid":2022541,"uid":346359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:28:53.000Z","msg":"請不推文 唔想上熱門 這是寵物台<br />\n請留熱門個位推27號煲底見文宣 立法會司法覆核 <br />\n不是借刀 我非打手非本人 謝絕是非不分 重點係隻貓到(請針對事) 以防起底 所有名會刪去 (勿相認)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如題 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EO4aP2J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEO4aP2J.png&h=f03f957e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PxEBLA4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPxEBLA4.png&h=85d31591&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cws0sPq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCws0sPq.png&h=a614e2cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uE8Gcf7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuE8Gcf7.png&h=91ba12f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n關係<br />\nA朋友 (家姐) B 朋友家姐個妹 C圖中貓主人 D 貓主人個妹. <br />\nA同C 唔識  B同D係同學<br />\n<br />\nA火遮眼 愛貓深切想屌醒C <br />\n冇direct貓主人<br />\n原因係貓主人已有幾張story 非意外搶食<br />\n故意同冇心之失係有分別 不多說<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w718BHV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw718BHV.jpg&h=d17f1adb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suZ2F9C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuZ2F9C.png&h=0998611f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n緊接住D睇到個post 打電話去屌B<br />\n傾電話嘅內容冇證據證明 不多説(以防以偏概全)<br />\n<br />\nC貓主出聲(回應A)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m642F9O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm642F9O.jpg&h=4fa757d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nA出聲 (回應C)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sjbTNRd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsjbTNRd.jpg&h=736432ad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0joCu4y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0joCu4y.jpg&h=0f0a953a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nC知道做錯收左聲 小學雞鬧架互屌(D煩住B A有幫B C幫D etc) <br />\n<br />\n旁觀者清(觀點)<br />\nA雞啄唔斷 係睇唔出C有悔意 <br />\nD 嘅ig 不停撩架 並非C所講嘅想完結成件事 <br />\n又或者C想完 <br />\nD卻唔受C嘅控制 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mw6gLC1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmw6gLC1.jpg&h=011baa26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下刪一千 (開始唔關事 針對其他野嚟噪)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇到最後 <br />\n希望所有巴絲嘅貓可以身體健康 養到肥肥白白 飲多啲水 <br />\n奉勸大家養寵物之前 諗清諗楚 唔好&rsquo;人有我有&rsquo;嘅心態 請領養代替購買<br />\n新手做貓奴 做好曬資料搜查 <br />\n買好貓咪所需嘅用品 係做主人嘅責任<br />\n養之前請三思而後行 <br />\n貓咪老左有病 需要人照顧 <br />\n需要大量時間金錢 同耐心<br />\n非一時打卡po ig開心而養寵物<br />\n請不要中途棄養 會好影響主子以後嘅發展<br />\n寵物嘅世界得你 你唔對佢好冇人對佢好<br />\n忠言逆耳 可選擇接受或參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffa9d19ddef555ae28d13dc3f8f941aaaf353fae","tid":2022541,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:30:21.000Z","msg":"養寵物都係為開心。。搞咁多嘢做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d385d4591c5ee824a645a2a2f406fcc685dc97f","tid":2022541,"uid":122590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:32:54.000Z","msg":"愛腦撚真係麻煩"},{"pid":"a1b6b6ea7e0c48f1b1e499f8ed59a938fd671343","tid":2022541,"uid":81698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:34:26.000Z","msg":"幾條港女互屌貼上連登把撚"},{"pid":"10f50dfe8f052334f6ec35e97fe842a18e82ef8e","tid":2022541,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:36:47.000Z","msg":"有冇懶人包"},{"pid":"0f2b53c4623e6c8dd7960a5b9b7c17e4d383baad","tid":2022541,"uid":270916,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:40:08.000Z","msg":"唔識養貓就咪撚養 周街都知動物唔食得人食嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=